{"tid":722481,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"《大黃蜂》導演背水一戰！失敗得回家繼承千億資產","createTime":"2018-06-29T14:20:22.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-06T14:06:22.000Z","uid":28765,"like":485,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":128,"replies":[{"pid":"2e8f803a5fca4c3f063643d3ff3f8a79c13d2c55","tid":722481,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-29T14:20:22.000Z","msg":"〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕<br />\n電影《變形金剛》第5集票房慘烈，系列作第6部電影《大黃蜂》找來只有拍過動畫片的導演崔維斯奈特（Travis Knight）。據了解，《大黃蜂》這部電影對崔維斯奈特意義重大，一旦他在電影產業失敗，就得繼承父親、NIKE創辦人菲爾奈特（Phil Knight）的307億美元（約新台幣9387億元）。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/liveNews/BigPic/600_phpkJbFgJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2FliveNews%2FBigPic%2F600_phpkJbFgJ.jpg&h=9739da77&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n《大黃蜂》電影導演崔維斯奈特（Travis Knight）。（歐新社資料照）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/liveNews/BigPic/600_php6qSShO.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2FliveNews%2FBigPic%2F600_php6qSShO.jpg&d=IRc0hK8F%2FdEAD2QkKYcFm%2F1gJfeR7%2BEkjjir5NquRfg%3D&h=fd7137d5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2FliveNews%2FBigPic%2F600_php6qSShO.jpg&h=fb5ddeee\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/liveNews/BigPic/600_php6qSShO.jpg</a><br />\nNIKE創辦人菲爾奈特（Phil Knight）。（法新社資料照）<br />\n<br />\n綜合媒體報導，崔維斯奈特身為全球知名運動品牌創辦的兒子，從小就背負「奈特之子」的巨大壓力。但崔維斯奈特執著想闖出一片天，高中畢業後，雖然拿到史丹佛大學的入學資格，但卻拒絕就讀這所名校，跑到紐約布魯克林以chilly TEE為藝名出了嘻哈專輯《離我遠點》，銷售量突破10萬張的好成績，但大部分的銷量都是父親私下貢獻的，甚至還傳出崔維斯奈特能夠出專輯，都是這靠父親去向唱片公司遊說。<br />\n<br />\n後來，崔維斯奈特以第一名的成績考入波特蘭州立大學，畢業後隱藏自己的背景，進入威爾&middot;文頓（Will Vinton）動畫廣告公司實習，並在此愛上定格動畫。不過，父親趁著威爾&middot;文頓面臨財務危機時，買下整間公司送給兒子，讓崔維斯奈特直接擔任董事長，公司後來改名為萊卡動畫工作室（Laika），該工作室的動畫作品先後獲得奧斯卡4次提名。現在崔維斯奈特接手《變形金剛》系列作，首次執導真人電影，對他而言是背水一戰，如果不好好努力，可能就要回去繼承百億美元家業。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2469219\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2469219&d=IRc0hK8F%2FdEAD2QkKYcFm%2F1gJfeR7%2BEkjjir5NquRfg%3D&h=67afb45a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2469219&h=8935e808\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2469219</a>"},{"pid":"fdd571668c0809f1d3c23c9b64a295f44ac50c84","tid":722481,"uid":37240,"like":1444,"dislike":5,"score":1439,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-29T14:23:36.000Z","msg":"我都想咁樣失敗，屌你老母！"},{"pid":"6700d4f29538b291b454c7b86729afee75e8ddb0","tid":722481,"uid":8219,"like":703,"dislike":5,"score":698,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-29T14:24:28.000Z","msg":"父幹得黎其實幾有性格<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"331551a51675fef00eff21ff4099bd4d50f52526","tid":722481,"uid":17368,"like":265,"dislike":2,"score":263,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-06-29T14:24:50.000Z","msg":"背水定背錢一戰？"},{"pid":"08aaf96deb8960630e7a1cce0dd68e2e79f1fcb6","tid":722481,"uid":28765,"like":405,"dislike":3,"score":402,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-29T14:28:25.000Z","msg":"NIKE, Inc. (NKE)<br />\nNYSE - Nasdaq Real Time Price. Currency in USD<br />\n<br />\n80.69+9.00 (+12.55%)<br />\nAs of 10:27AM EDT. Market open.<br />\n<br />\n老豆今日又多左十幾廿億美金<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e4d3aa984dd845f3a6fba1b406874bc2b19244b9","tid":722481,"uid":36478,"like":140,"dislike":0,"score":140,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-29T14:29:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"91b88c240b59a61ca069c8948709b1597421ebd6","tid":722481,"uid":3358,"like":442,"dislike":1,"score":441,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-29T14:31:20.000Z","msg":"大家做兄弟既唔洗講咁多<br />\n呢獲野我幫你繼承左佢"},{"pid":"7e7c96e8317d24df7b2cb7fc79cf202150da7932","tid":722481,"uid":53687,"like":142,"dislike":2,"score":140,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-29T14:31:32.000Z","msg":"衰咗會爭人周身債先好話係背水啦"},{"pid":"ec9f1902f7459edbb9c1ede6457f46b37393b989","tid":